title: AT THE WINNERS' TABLE: An MFCEO Q&A Show, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO271
itunes:title: AT THE WINNERS' TABLE: An MFCEO Q&A Show, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO271
description: We got the four winners of the MFCEO iTunes Review Contest - Carly Damuth, Chris De Brock, Dr. Tom Recher, and Carmella Goslar - & they asked some incredibly practical & thoughtful questions about business & success that are relevant to anybody, at any stage in their journey. From "how service businesses can get their clients to pay them on time" to "how to leverage Amazon without being dependent on it," this is a high quality, high content conversation with a lot of fun, wisdom, & even some vulnerability.
